---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About" description="Learn about CyberInventors — why we track cybersecurity startups.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">About CyberInventors</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc mt-10 max-w-none">
      <p>
        CyberInventors is an independent directory and news aggregator focused
        on the emerging cybersecurity startup ecosystem. We track companies
        building the tools, platforms, and services that will define how
        organizations defend themselves over the next decade.
      </p>

      <h2>Why We Exist</h2>
      <p>
        The cybersecurity vendor landscape is overwhelming. Hundreds of new
        companies emerge every year, and it's hard to separate signal from noise.
        CyberInventors curates the most interesting startups — filtering for
        genuine innovation, not just marketing spend.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Track</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Early-stage startups (pre-seed through Series B)</li>
        <li>Companies solving novel or underserved problems</li>
        <li>Founders with deep domain expertise</li>
        <li>Products with real customer traction</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Submit a Company</h2>
      <p>
        Know a company we should be covering?{" "}
        <a href="/submit">Submit it here</a> and we'll review it for inclusion in
        the directory.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
